{
  "stem": "2353.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was very hard, very tough.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And to find somebody to sponsor you was almost impossible, because they would-- would have been responsible for you if you couldn't have found a job.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So they would have had to support you financially.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And people weren't that anxious to do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I borrowed $2,000 from different sources. $10 here, $100 there, until I got $2,000.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's the minimum that the consulate, the American consulate, asked for for an affidavit.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I made out the papers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they-- they-- they approved it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I returned all the money again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he's really here under-- under false pretenses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he did all right, served in the Army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He couldn't wait to get into the Army, into the American Army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So when he went down to you know, to-- to enroll, they said they wouldn't take him as an officer, because he was not a citizen yet.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But he could go in as a private.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But that he didn't want to do, because he had a friend who was also a doctor.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he went in as a private.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And instead of employing him somewhere in-- in the medical field, they made him shovel coal or some-- I mean, some-- some really stupid things.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my husband said, I think I can do more good to work in a hospital than to-- to do some meaningless job.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And soon, I think the same day that he got his citizenship, he went down to Whitehall, and he got his commission as a first lieutenant.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was still an enemy alien, even though he came a year after me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the Army needed doctors, so I guess they processed him a little faster.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
